⚙️ Installation Guide (MT4)

Follow these steps to install the indicator in MetaTrader 4:

1. Download the Indicator
Download the .ex4 file from this repository.

2. Open MT4 Data Folder
Open MetaTrader 4
In the top menu, click:
File → Open Data Folder

3. Navigate to Indicators Folder
Go to:
MQL4 → Indicators

4. Add the File
Copy and paste the downloaded indicator file into the Indicators folder

5. Restart MT4 (recommended)
Close and reopen MetaTrader 4
(or right-click in Navigator → Refresh)

6. Apply the Indicator
In MT4, open the Navigator panel
Expand Indicators
Drag and drop the indicator onto your chart
(or double-click it)

7. Recommended Setup
Use the indicator on the EUR/USD chart
Timeframe can be adjusted based on your trading style
